title: The Depp Heard Round The World
itunes:title: The Depp Heard Round The World
description:
Team Good For You puts on their big girl pants to discuss the Johnny Depp/Amber Heard verdict through the lens of love addiction, codependence, and self-destruction and give advice on how to extricate yourself from the morass of a toxic relationship.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
